521
00:37:12,400 --> 00:37:14,800
Oh.
Well, that's too bad, isn't it?

522
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:16,900
I just thought you'd like to know.

523
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:19,300
Yeah, well, I appreciate you calling.

524
00:37:19,400 --> 00:37:21,000
Okay.

525
00:37:22,100 --> 00:37:24,100
[ Phone Clicks, Beeps ]

526
00:37:52,000 --> 00:37:53,700
Bo!
[ Groans ]

527
00:38:06,900 --> 00:38:08,900
[ Sighs ]

528
00:38:13,400 --> 00:38:16,300
All right.

529
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:18,400
Okay.

