793
00:57:45,400 --> 00:57:47,400
Go home!

794
00:57:47,500 --> 00:57:50,400
Check your monitor.
See if Laramie's found the cameras.

795
00:57:50,500 --> 00:57:52,400
I gotta think this through.

796
00:57:52,500 --> 00:57:54,700
Go home.
I'll call you later.

