807
00:58:35,800 --> 00:58:38,200
<i>I'm goin;</i>
<i>Not waitin'for y'all.</i>

808
00:58:38,300 --> 00:58:41,400
dd [ Continues ]

809
00:58:48,300 --> 00:58:50,200
- What's going on, man?
- [ Gasps ]

810
00:58:50,300 --> 00:58:51,900
You!

811
00:58:52,000 --> 00:58:54,900
- Yo, you Bo, right? You Bo, right?
- Yeah.

812
00:58:55,000 --> 00:58:57,000
[ Laughs ]
This your crib!

813
00:58:57,100 --> 00:58:59,400
Yeah. What do I owe you
for the pizza?

814
00:58:59,500 --> 00:59:01,400
You don't owe me nothin'.

815
00:59:01,500 --> 00:59:05,400
Just send down one of them bad white bitches,
and you can have all the pizza you want.

816
00:59:05,500 --> 00:59:08,300
All right, tell you what.
Here's $60.

817
00:59:08,400 --> 00:59:10,300
- All right?
- Yo, thanks a lot, man.

