01:00:15,400 --> 01:00:18,400
<i>Yeah, it's Burton. How's Vic comin'</i>
<i>with that Leonard Clark tape?</i>

824
01:00:22,000 --> 01:00:23,800
No kidding.

825
01:00:23,900 --> 01:00:26,900
- Tell him to cue it up. I'll be right in.
- [ Beeps ]

826
01:00:31,600 --> 01:00:33,500
There you go, chief.

827
01:00:33,600 --> 01:00:35,500
Well, I'll be a son of a bitch.

828
01:00:35,600 --> 01:00:37,800
- Can I get a copy of this?
- Copy?

829
01:00:38,000 --> 01:00:40,300
I can give it to you on DVD.

830
01:00:45,700 --> 01:00:48,000
I'm gonna go wake up Laramie.

