864
01:05:48,600 --> 01:05:50,500
What is this?

865
01:05:51,800 --> 01:05:53,700
Impound found
some video equipment...

866
01:05:53,800 --> 01:05:55,700
in the back of Leonard's car.

867
01:05:55,800 --> 01:05:59,800
Seems he was wearing a miniature camera
when he came to the set.

868
01:06:04,600 --> 01:06:06,500
