870
01:06:30,000 --> 01:06:32,600
<i>[ Burton ]</i>
<i>Okay, now...</i>

871
01:06:32,700 --> 01:06:34,700
watch this very closely.

872
01:06:37,400 --> 01:06:39,100
<i>[ Burton ]</i>
<i>There.</i>

